    "updated_at": "2015-01-26T18:48:15Z",
    "body": "You should show the window when page is ready (namely `document.onready`), not when app is ready.\n\n> Also the hide and show options and methods don't work for fullscreen windows so you can't use them for this bug.\n\nYou can call the `setFullScreen` API after the page is ready.\n"
